                        <li>Register or sign-up to use a service.</li>
                        <li>Subscribe to a newsletter or desire to be added to our mailing lists for other products and services.</li>
                        <li>Place an order.</li>
                        <li>Provide feedback in an online survey.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>In each of the instances above, we typically ask for your name, e-mail address, phone number, address, Log in Name and Password, as well as, other similar personal information that is needed to register or subscribe you to services or offers. On occasion, we may ask for additional information to enable us to provide you with access to and use of certain information, materials and services. In the case of newsletters or mailing lists, you will be able to "unsubscribe" to these mailers at any time. </p>
                    <p>Wherever Talent Orientations collects personal information we make an effort to include a link to this Privacy Policy on that page.</p>

